column5: I’m not contemplating. I just have these thoughts. There’s a difference.

Yes. I do this w coworkers and have done so in the past on social media before I deactivated it all. I literally was just talking to a friend about this. It’s like you know you’re doing it while you do it, but you can’t stop. I absolutely hate it
Outside of social media. Try as hard as you can. It’s possible. 💕
